{"tid":2017990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡雅文法官：示威者導致警民關係惡化","createTime":"2020-05-15T11:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T12:43:10.000Z","uid":246828,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c9de9738e6c0eebdd082125f5dc8979f9e2f02ee","tid":2017990,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2019/DCCC000783_2019.docx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fjudg%2Fword%2Fvetted%2Fother%2Fen%2F2019%2FDCCC000783_2019.docx&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=841912a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2019/DCCC000783_2019.docx</a><br />\n<br />\n61. I also take the view that <span style=\"color: red;\"> a repeated attack on the police in the due execution of their duties, their duty to protect the Legislative Council, which led to a riot at the doors of the Legislature of Hong Kong was a direct attack on the rule of law </span> which undoubtedly caused harm. Such criminal conduct showed no respect for law and order nor the safety of law enforcement officers.<br />\n <br />\n62. I have also considered <span style=\"color: red;\"> the scale of the disturbance that afternoon </span> caused to the public, the harm to society, <span style=\"color: red;\"> including the relation between the police and the public </span> as well as public expenditure resulting from it. Without a doubt, the present case was a very serious one.<br />\n <br />\n63. Accordingly, the defendant&rsquo;s mitigation and personal circumstances are not mitigating factors of any significant weight."},{"pid":"57d1ef0e4ff3831e2e5e7aa04b637fc199e32d3b","tid":2017990,"uid":142965,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:10:16.000Z","msg":"示威者唔係市民?"},{"pid":"518b80425de002343b1917a0733c7f466f0413fa","tid":2017990,"uid":184581,"l